Straitway Cult Members Daniel and Kristin Muir post bail $5,000 each | Did P.Diddy Dowell Pay?

In this video we address a Pastor who slandered my name with a vicious lie.  

In this video we share our commentary and criticism to teach and educate our community about the subject matter in the video title which cover news reporting, dating, relationships issues, REVIEWS and more for deep conversations to stimulate thought.

► About me and my work:

I’m RINGO aka RINGOTV Reactions formerly known BlackMaleAdviceTV on my older videos. I’m the Content Creator of the channel. I have over 17 years of experience on Youtube making content.  We provide the best commentary, criticism, educational reaction content, deep discussions about the topics you want to hear about. Our YouTube videos are very entertaining and educational with humor at times. We love to offer advice and make sense of things that are hard to understand for most people. We talk about dating, marriage, news stories, unsolved crimes, entertainment news and many more topics. My content is creative and unique due too the time and energy added to break things down for viewers to think by using my voice. I’m also a professional music producer and video editor. I’m all about Creativity and learning new things to be a better Creator. As you enter the classroom be sure to click the Like button, notification bell for ALL and subscribe today and leave a comment after viewing my video. Thanks for your support and viewership.
